docs.title: Welcome to Años de Andy
docs.text: Welcome to my archive. A simple guide to the music, mixes, collaborations I've created over the years. Bonus photo archive as well.

docs.title: July 2025 – Building the Archive
docs.text: Lately I've been reflecting on how much material I’ve created over the years and how best to organize it. This site is a simple container—a way to keep things accessible without overloading the senses. At the moment everything is kind of spread amongs multiple platforms so I've uploaded everything to Bandcamp. Which, even with it's outdated UI, is the best platform for artist and listener. Everything you aquire is stored in your account and you can stream it via the app.
